AoW and the planes aren't even remotely the same level.  A Guardian of Fire in Sol Ro Tower easily outdamages AoW when unslowed and you've to tank two of those at once.  <br>
An AoW capable guild is a far cry from Emperor ready, and most certainly not mega DPS machine of doom PoP uber ready.  <br>
<br>
For the planes, there's plenty of xp places just people aren't willing to spread out.<br>
<br>
Bastion of Thunder can support at least 4 groups.  I'll bet you can easily fit 2 groups under each wing assuming no mage pet of doom is rampaging through the area.<br>
<br>
Tactics can probably support 3 groups in the Arena after the charm nerf.<br>
<br>
HoH is boring but it's still solid xp, can probably support 4-5 groups, again assuming no soloing enchanters.<br>
<br>
